info.name: Ai Tenchi Muyou!
info.description: The franchise is celebrating its 20th anniversary with this new project. In this story, the world is in chaos, thanks to Washu. Now in order to save it, Tenchi Masaki must go undercover as a student teacher at an all-girls school. Unfortunately for him, trouble always comes his way as he has a hard time dealing with the hijinks of his new students.
